query:
INSERT INTO debounce_key (job_id, key)
                  VALUES ($1, $2)
                  ON CONFLICT (key)
                  DO UPDATE SET
                      previous_job_id = debounce_key.job_id,
                      job_id = EXCLUDED.job_id, -- replace current job with new one 
                      debounced_times = debounce_key.debounced_times + 1 -- evaluated only if conflict,
                      -- conflict means there is already existing value,
                      -- which means overriding it will also imply adding new entry to v2_job_debounce_batch and thus debouncing the job
                      -- so the counter should be incremented
                  RETURNING
                      debounced_times,
                      first_started_at,
                      previous_job_id AS job_id_to_debounce
